The Contractor for the&nbsp;I-40 Project at the Davie-Forsyth County Line is scheduled to close the left lane of I-40 Westbound and I-40 Eastbound between NC 801 (Exit 180) to Harper Road (Exit 182). These closures are scheduled nightly for Wednesday night August 25th from 6:00pm - 5:00am (Eastbound) and 7:00pm - 7:00am (Westbound). These lane closures will be utilized for pavement marking operations. This work is part of the&nbsp;continuing construction to&nbsp;replace the I-40 bridges over the Yadkin River and to widen and make improvements along I-40.&nbsp;As always this work is weather dependent and may be subject to change.
